{"tid":823863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味點解仲有班廢老出嚟同人逼","createTime":"2018-09-17T01:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T06:02:10.000Z","uid":3900,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4085b1b5bbf9c05c50db2905b59cf19ca4a6e657","tid":823863,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:32:34.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 返去訓棺材"},{"pid":"da4627dcfc6d3809a1f2b1204d2e8b2ca7c368dc","tid":823863,"uid":73878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:41:01.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n一早喺屯門出九龍<br />\n又無接駁巴士去西鐵<br />\n又無狗巴<br />\n<br />\n唯有行去輕鐵站轉西鐵<br />\n<br />\n途中又冧樹<br />\n行人路要捐嗰啲樹先過到<br />\n<br />\n以上一切我都算啦<br />\n<br />\n去到西鐵站樓下竟然見到班大媽喺度跳廣場舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭輕鐵嗰陣時啲阿婆又一早推住架買餸車。<br />\n趕住去買餸，好似會 飢荒 咁<br />\n<br />\n今朝交通已經混亂搭所有鐵喇沙甸魚一樣<br />\n<br />\n再加埋班廢老。<br />\n真係火都嚟埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06498f66da6f14add1ff0b1862a7dd5fdc2e8bc2","tid":823863,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4085b1b5bbf9c05c50db2905b59cf19ca4a6e657","tid":823863,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:32:34.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 返去訓棺材"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:41:35.000Z","msg":"樓主真係可憐<br />\n靠屌班老人嚟刷存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91e053e414aec2d96cb59aa02271d419d7a5ed2","tid":823863,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgm